pageContext.claim: “And I hate to do this to you, I was having a great hair day, and then I heard you had 40-mile an hour winds up, look. Then I said all right give me the cap. I don't do [wear a MAGA cap] often, but now I'm looking at that beautiful sight.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump is often photographed wearing a his campaign's trademark "Make America Great Again'" cap.
